<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="right-n">right <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /raɪt/    美 /raɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 正确：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the difference between right and wrong 
是与非的区别</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[常用单数] 右侧；右边：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The boy looked to the right. 
那男孩朝右边看了看。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>on sb’s right</strong> 
在某人的右侧</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c-u">3.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 权利：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I believe that children <strong>have the right</strong> to live in a world that is safe. 
我认为孩子们有权生活在一个安全的世界中。</p><footer>2008 辽宁</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>rightly /'raɪtli/ adv   </p></div>